斯蘭教法領導者，以各種各樣的理由消滅另一穆斯林派別。這樣的國家為：阿富汗 100%、索馬里 100%、也門100%。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唯有等新一代的元首出黎消滅伊斯蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1c0e9c057d468cec2240a09173386dcf501583","tid":435509,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T22:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>共用祈禱室有乜問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你高級過人地？<br />\n耶教對著你地班生番就真係覺得不受專重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n逼人就晒佢哋就真喇 咁佢哋有無尊重其他人先 成日詐詐諦諦攞特權"},{"pid":"a8c1f3638a1ac52298083496513d7e32ad8ddfe0","tid":435509,"uid":28397,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T22:23:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人接受能力好低 又唔肯去學習伊斯蘭教文化</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除咗一夫多妻 無嘢值得學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ceca75989aaa45736a2be470c4f545f770c83ae","tid":435509,"uid":130060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T22:25:56.000Z","msg":"點解唔係班清真撚屌去人地方適應人地習俗同文化 要香港人就番佢地咁反智 訓醒未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0beebf5fbc0afc93ef1a304bfb25ef235b9e2163","tid":435509,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T22:25:58.000Z","msg":"融你老尾, 切條豬賓州塞入你個臭閪嘴"},{"pid":"9aa07b9bfc513090a6008b518affe2dce8812c62","tid":435509,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T22:26:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然支那政府係仆街，但佢地打壓回教係有一手</blockquote><br />\n但願唔會出反效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64937070ecbd3728b4b2f74b3c162185a58ac5c8","tid":435509,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T22:33:15.000Z","msg":"你學人地生活方式咪融入到囉，你話揾工比人歧視就話啫，飲食同祈禱要人黎就你？你痴撚左線呀？你自己帶飯同咪撚揾工啦！最好就返去